 * GP0_2 -> 3.3V
 * GP0_3 -> GPIO1_25 -> MOSI
 * GP0_4 -> GPIO1_17 -> MISO
 * GP0_5 -> GPIO3_20 -> SCLK
 * GP0_6 -> GPIO3_17 -> CS
